These are Puzzles for 4x4 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-2-1::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: musical, drama, spy, satire
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: gospel, house, d&b, jazz
There are 4 different nationalities: spanish, egyptian, japanese, pakistani
The people use 4 different means of transport: subway, bike, skateboard, car
1. the egyptian is the fan of jazz##1
2. the japanese is between the person watching spy movies and the person watching satire movies##2
3. the egyptian is the person driving the subway##1
4. the person driving the car is on the left of the person driving the subway##1
5. the fan of gospel is on the left of the spanish##1
6. the person driving the skateboard is the person watching spy movies##1
7. the fan of house is on the left of the person watching satire movies##1
8. the spanish is on the far right##1
9. the person watching drama movies is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2     |     3      |    4     |
| Movie-Genre   | drama | satire   | musical  | spy  |
| Music-Genre   | house    | jazz    | gospel      | d&b    |
| Nationality   | pakistani | egyptian | japanese | spanish |
| Transport     | car  | subway       | bike    | skateboard     |

