.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-2-2::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: video-games, photography, skydiving, chess
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: time-travel, spy, zombie, drama
4 different pets are kept: turtle, hamster, pony, mouse
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: badminton, cricket, snowboarding, skiing
1. the person who's sport is skiing is on the right of the person who's hobby is chess##1
2. the person who's hobby is video-games is on the far right##1
3. the owner of the mouse is the person who's sport is cricket##1
4. the person who's hobby is skydiving is on the right of the person who's hobby is photography##1
5. the person watching drama movies is between the owner of the pony and the person who's sport is badminton##2
6. the person who's sport is skiing is between the person watching drama movies and the owner of the mouse##2
7. the owner of the turtle is on the far right##1
8. the person watching spy movies is on the left of the person who's hobby is skydiving##1
9. the person watching zombie movies is on the right of the owner of the hamster##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |    3     |     4      |
| Hobby         | chess | photography    | skydiving  | video-games    |
| Movie-Genre   | time-travel      | spy  | drama  | zombie |
| Pet           | mouse      | pony       | hamster      | turtle       |
| Sport         | cricket    | skiing | snowboarding | badminton |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-2-3::.
There 4 different types of food: kale, watermelon, cauliflower, cabbage
The people have 4 different hobbies: puzzles, gardening, dancing, writing
The people have 4 different jobs:  electrician, manager, writer, nurse
The people use 4 different means of transport: scooter, boat, car, ship
1. the writer is the person driving the boat##1
2. the person driving the boat is on the left of the nurse##1
3. the person driving the car is on the left of the person driving the boat##1
4. the person driving the boat is on the left of the person driving the scooter##1
5. the person eating cauliflower is on the left of the person who's hobby is dancing##1
6. the manager is the person who's hobby is writing##1
7. the person eating cabbage is on the right of the person who's hobby is dancing##1
8. the person eating kale is between the person who's hobby is puzzles and the person who's hobby is writing##2
9. the person who's hobby is dancing is between the person eating cauliflower and the manager##2

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |     2     |      3      |     4     |
| Food        | watermelon | cauliflower     | kale   | cabbage     |
| Hobby       | gardening   | puzzles   | dancing | writing |
| Job         | electrician   | writer | nurse       | manager    |
| Transport   | car    | boat | scooter  | ship    |

