.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-2-4::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  dressmaker, entrepreneur, firefighter, designer
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: romance, western, spy, family
4 different pets are kept: turtle, mouse, chinchilla, horse
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: swimming, badminton, sailing, weightlifting
 1. the person watching western movies is on the far right##1
 2. the person watching family movies is the dressmaker##1
 3. the owner of the turtle is on the right of the person who's sport is weightlifting##1
 4. the person who's sport is swimming is on the far left##1
 5. the person watching family movies is the owner of the mouse##1
 6. the owner of the horse is on the right of the person who's sport is swimming##1
 7. the person watching western movies is the firefighter##1
 8. the person watching romance movies is on the right of the person watching family movies##1
 9. the dressmaker is on the left of the person who's sport is badminton##1
10. the entrepreneur is between the owner of the turtle and the designer##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |      3       |       4        |
| Job           | dressmaker  | designer | entrepreneur     | firefighter |
| Movie-Genre   | family | romance  | spy | western       |
| Pet           | mouse       | horse    | chinchilla      | turtle           |
| Sport         | swimming | badminton   | weightlifting   | sailing         |

