.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-2-5::.
There 4 different types of food: pineapple, apple, radish, pepper
The people have 4 different jobs:  librarian, chef, accountant, analyst
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: musical, drama, family, superhero
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: cycling, skiing, rugby, badminton
 1. the person eating radish is on the right of the person eating apple##1
 2. the person who's sport is cycling is on the far left##1
 3. the accountant is the person eating apple##1
 4. the accountant is on the left of the person who's sport is rugby##1
 5. the person watching superhero movies is on the left of the person eating pepper##1
 6. the person eating radish is on the left of the person watching superhero movies##1
 7. the analyst is on the left of the person eating pineapple##1
 8. the chef is the person watching drama movies##1
 9. the person eating radish is between the person who's sport is badminton and the person watching musical movies##2
10. the person watching family movies is the person who's sport is rugby##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1        |       2       |       3       |     4      |
| Food          | apple         | radish         | pineapple     | pepper      |
| Job           | accountant | analyst | librarian    | chef     |
| Movie-Genre   | musical      | family       | superhero    | drama       |
| Sport         | cycling     | rugby       | badminton | skiing |

