3. the owner of the hedgehog is on the left of the owner of the guinea-pig##1
4. the person driving the motorbike is on the left of the person drinking almond-milk##1
5. the person driving the skateboard is between the person driving the ship and the person watching disaster movies##2
6. the person drinking mirinda is the person watching crime movies##1
7. the person drinking 7up is on the left of the owner of the goat##1
8. the person drinking milk is on the left of the person drinking almond-milk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |      3      |   4    |
| Beverage      | mirinda  | 7up   | milk    | almond-milk  |
| Movie-Genre   | crime    | horror   | disaster | mystery |
| Pet           | hedgehog       | guinea-pig   | goat        | fish  |
| Transport     | ship | skateboard | motorbike         | van |

