 1. the person eating radish is the electrician##1
 2. the person eating kale is the person who's sport is skiing##1
 3. the electrician is the person who's sport is swimming##1
 4. the person eating pear is on the right of the person eating kale##1
 5. the fan of disco is the person eating blueberry##1
 6. the fan of classical is on the far left##1
 7. the software-developer is on the left of the electrician##1
 8. the fan of blues is on the far right##1
 9. the chef is between the mechanic and the person who's sport is soccer##2
10. the person eating kale is on the left of the person eating pear##1

