.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-2-10::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, milk, 7up, juice
There 4 different types of food: apricot, zucchini, spinach, apple
The people have 4 different hobbies: writing, magic-tricks, skydiving, chess
4 different pets are kept: guinea-pig, frog, hedgehog, fish
 1. the person drinking 7up is on the right of the person drinking milk##1
 2. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the right of the owner of the hedgehog##1
 3. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is on the right of the person who's hobby is chess##1
 4. the person eating apricot is the person drinking milk##1
 5. the person drinking almond-milk is on the right of the person drinking juice##1
 6. the person who's hobby is writing is on the right of the person eating apricot##1
 7. the owner of the hedgehog is on the left of the person drinking almond-milk##1
 8. the owner of the fish is between the person eating apricot and the person eating spinach##2
 9. the person eating apple is on the right of the owner of the frog##1
10. the person who's hobby is writing is between the person eating apricot and the person eating spinach##2

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |     2      |      3      |       4       |
| Beverage   | milk    | 7up    | juice      | almond-milk |
| Food       | apricot        | apple       | spinach       | zucchini     |
| Hobby      | skydiving | writing | chess | magic-tricks        |
| Pet        | frog       | fish     | hedgehog         | guinea-pig           |

