 4. the owner of the pony is on the right of the person eating peach##1
 5. the owner of the pony is between the owner of the frog and the owner of the hedgehog##2
 6. the person driving the roller is on the left of the person who's sport is surfing##1
 7. the person who's sport is skiing is the person eating strawberry##1
 8. the person driving the taxi is on the far right##1
 9. the owner of the hedgehog is the person driving the bike##1
10. the person who's sport is soccer is the person eating apricot##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |    2     |    3     |     4      |
