 3. the polish is between the person eating plum and the person eating apple##2
 4. the person eating pineapple is on the right of the person watching sports movies##1
 5. the person watching epic movies is on the far left##1
 6. the person drinking tea is on the right of the person eating grapes##1
 7. the person eating plum is on the far right##1
 8. the person watching scientific movies is on the right of the pakistani##1
 9. the person drinking water is the polish##1
10. the person drinking tea is on the left of the person watching scientific movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2       |     3      |    4     |
| Beverage      | soy-milk     | tea         | water   | almond-milk |
| Food          | grapes | apple    | pineapple   | plum   |
| Movie-Genre   | epic   | sports | scientific   | crime   |
| Nationality   | french | pakistani     | polish | mexican |

 